-- Position Management :
 - Most Control
 - A position is created to be filled by one worker
 - Position must be approved and available
 - A "chair" can be empty or filled, must be available to bring someone in
 - A "chair" has its own characteristics

-- Job Management :
 - Most flexibility/spped
 - Hiring restrictions are set for the entire org
 - No defined quantity for number of jobs available

